data.description: All about privacy! This 4b/2.5b home is located at the dead end of a quiet country road. Built in 2001, this beautiful home is a mix of both country and modern, just waiting for you to make her your new dream home. Master bed and bath, walk in shower and a jacuzzi tub, are located downstairs with the remaining 3 bedrooms and 2nd full bathroom located upstairs. With 2 living areas, formal dining and huge kitchen, there's plenty of space for everyone. The west half of the property is a horse pen with security lighting as well as a multi use feed shed/ outbuilding. Just 45 minutes from downtown OKC, you can enjoy the country with easy access to the city. Property is 2 lots, totaling 4.5+ acres. All appliances will remain with the property. Seller reserves the hot tub.
